  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "id": "6e28e26d-83ab-4d6c-bb6b-8061e59bf5fc",
      "paper_id": "a0da80f9-4831-4939-b5f8-4d76839c782d",
      "section_id": null,
      "order": 0,
      "text": "Ada Researcher, Grace Scientist",
      "bounding_boxes": [
        {
          "page_number": 1,
          "x0": 78.0,
          "y0": 124.82000000000005,
          "x1": 223.61,
          "y1": 134.07000000000005
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "1fc5f4e9-2d82-4508-a374-6a7b667a9888",
      "paper_id": "a0da80f9-4831-4939-b5f8-4d76839c782d",
      "section_id": "493745ab-5d84-45c4-8024-85ea251cef88",
      "order": 0,
      "text": "Scientific papers contain rich multimodal information including text, tables, and figures. Understanding this information requires a system that can jointly reason over all modalities.",
      "bounding_boxes": [
        {
          "page_number": 1,
          "x0": 78.0,
          "y0": 252.82000000000005,
          "x1": 527.6299999999999,
          "y1": 274.07000000000005
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "32093e71-fcb8-48a2-93e4-1b723a381dab",
      "paper_id": "a0da80f9-4831-4939-b5f8-4d76839c782d",
      "section_id": "493745ab-5d84-45c4-8024-85ea251cef88",
      "order": 1,
      "text": "In this work we propose a pipeline that parses a PDF into a structured representation before any retrieval or generation takes place.",
      "bounding_boxes": [
        {
          "page_number": 1,
          "x0": 78.0,
          "y0": 276.82000000000005,
          "x1": 503.19999999999976,
          "y1": 298.07
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "bd424529-4d52-4f69-ab75-68974fde777c",
      "paper_id": "a0da80f9-4831-4939-b5f8-4d76839c782d",
      "section_id": "1e6ac466-99c8-4601-bfaa-f52e68de5c1f",
      "order": 0,
      "text": "Our method consists of four stages: ingestion, parsing, chunking, and retrieval.",
      "bounding_boxes": [
        {
          "page_number": 1,
          "x0": 78.0,
          "y0": 340.82,
          "x1": 425.94,
          "y1": 350.07
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "2eea2186-42b6-4ed9-bf88-f69541641bba",
      "paper_id": "a0da80f9-4831-4939-b5f8-4d76839c782d",
      "section_id": "8bb8032a-4d25-412c-b46e-2456b4f0c617",
      "order": 0,
      "text": "The parsing stage converts a raw PDF into sections, paragraphs, tables, and figures using a document layout model.",
      "bounding_boxes": [
        {
          "page_number": 1,
          "x0": 78.0,
          "y0": 388.82,
          "x1": 532.0999999999998,
          "y1": 410.07
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "4552ee08-29a9-439f-8154-18f21809bb50",
      "paper_id": "a0da80f9-4831-4939-b5f8-4d76839c782d",
      "section_id": "6f43773f-871a-470b-a739-edd6ea4b29d0",
      "order": 0,
      "text": "We presented a parsing pipeline for scientific documents and showed its role in a larger multimodal question answering system.",
      "bounding_boxes": [
        {
          "page_number": 2,
          "x0": 78.0,
          "y0": 62.82000000000005,
          "x1": 515.95,
          "y1": 84.07000000000005
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
